    Configuration Parameter interface for configuring the Raft consensus system Any component using this implementation might want to provide an implementation of this interface to configure A default implementation will be used if none is provided.
    PeerAddressResolver
    Interface to resolve raft actor peer addresses.
    RaftActor
    RaftActor encapsulates a state machine that needs to be kept synchronized in a cluster.

    Interface for a class that participates in raft actor persistence recovery.
    RaftActorSnapshotCohort
    Interface for a class that participates in raft actor snapshotting.
